column1: Traffic reports will resume Thursday March 7 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: All outbound lanes are shut down at Patchen Wilkes Dr until further notice due to a collision near Frederick Douglass HS.
Traffic is being diverted to Patchen Wilkes Dr to Meeting St to Sir Barton Way.
Motorists traveling outbound on Winchester Rd should use New Circle Rd if possible.
